description.en: Murphy is a 12 year old siberian cat who’s life recently turned upside down, in a good way. He was found and adopted by $MURPHY's CEO and owner of this project. MURPHYCAT, community driven project, aims to produce rapsongs, cartoon NFTs in addition to that juicy USDT rewards for holding $Murphy. This is more than just a memetoken. They will release every few weeks a new cartoon about MURPHY. Soon they will have their own NFT-marketplace!
